Package: utf8
Title: Portable Tools for 'UTF-8' Character Data
Date: 2017-10-23
Version: 0.0-16
Authors@R: person("Kirill", "MÃ¼ller", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "krlmlr+r@mailbox.org")
Description:
    Implements an S3 class for storing 'UTF-8' strings, based on regular characters vectors.
    Also contains routines to portably read and write 'UTF-8' encoded text files, and create character vectors with various encodings.
